rows.label: qst003402_msg0002
rows.name:
So, you had to break the
water tower to get away from
the Superbian soldiers?

rows.label: qst003402_msg0003
rows.name: It's sort of their fault then, really.

rows.label: qst003402_msg0004
rows.name:
I can't really blame you
lot for something you did
when you were cornered.

rows.label: qst003402_msg0005
rows.name:
Ah, nothing changes, does it? These
mighty forces do what they like, and
us little fellows pay the price.

rows.label: qst003402_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey, aren't you the ones who brought
that Melosian Honey earlier?

rows.label: qst003402_msg0007
rows.name:
My daughter's not got much of an
appetite, but she can't resist ruska
cookies with a bit of Melosian Honey.

rows.label: qst003402_msg0008
rows.name:
I suppose I can let you off
that argy-bargy with the water
tower, for bringing us that.

rows.label: qst003402_msg0009
rows.name:
But next time you're taking on that
Superbian bunch, try and spare a
thought for the rest of us, yeah?
